ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS Supreme Court of Ohio. March 12, 2018

Proposed amendments to the Supreme Court Rules for the Government of the Bar of Ohio (Gov.Bar R. VI, Sec. 11 and Appendix I) will be published in the March 12, 2018 Ohio Official Reports advance sheet for a public-comment period ending April 11, 2018.

O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, and DeGenaro, JJ., concurred in publishing the proposed amendments for comment.
